applicationModel.name: example-editable-table
applicationModel.description: This application contains a fully-editable table showing persons working in enterprises. Each person can be edited in-place by clicking on the table rows. Expanding the table row shows more details, including a map where the person is geolocalized. Persons are persisted in a storage. A simple search field allows searching the enterprises in the table.
